'''''Farther Than The Snow Plains''''' is a [[Companion Mission]] in the chapter [[Slices of Life Before the Furnace]].

==Steps==
# Find a suitable camping spot
# Establish the camp
# Ask whether Pela can fix the heater
# Collect the Geomarrow Activation Element and food
# Return to the camp and prepare dinner
# Ascertain the abnormality in the camp
# (Optional) Take a picture of the mysterious creature
# (Optional) Eliminate the mysterious creature
# Investigate the item left by the mysterious creature
# Fix the heater
# Cook dinner with Lynx
# Wait for the aurora with Lynx
# Talk with everyone
# View the aurora

